name: 01. GREED
description:
4/7 from "7 Deadly Sins" collection.

I hope to move around wherever they guide me, in this case I just follow orders; whatever you want to give me, what i need;
the important things to live in this world: just papers and stamps, discovered feelings, gold chains, the fever for the ego. 
I stop myself to think if the road I am taking is the one I want to be on. Holding hands, the sun goes down over the mountain,
all of a sudden a torrential rain visits us and just like that it disappears. 
Only the water on my body and that cold between my fingers, reminds me about that moment.

Full story: naranjabrasa.com
